[P1_1_1_InterrogateDialog]
Speech_0001L=FISHER - I need information. 
Speech_0002L=MILITIAN - I... I don't speak English.
Speech_0003L=FISHER - I'd be willing to bet your neck that you do.
Speech_0004L=MILITIAN - I know a little English.
Speech_0005L=FISHER - Good to hear.  I'm going inside to meet your friends.  Anything I need to worry about?
Speech_0006L=MILITIAN - They have guns.
Speech_0007L=FISHER - I'm shocked and amazed.  What else?
Speech_0032L=MILITIAN - My men planted the mines on our way out.  We had to escort... to defend the village.
Speech_0012L=FISHER - Escort who?
Speech_0013L=MILITIAN - Nothing.
Speech_0014L=FISHER - Escort who?
Speech_0015L=MILITIAN - Nobody.  I made a mistake.
Speech_0016L=FISHER - Escort who?
Speech_0017L=MILITIAN - I don't know his name.  Somebody important to Sadono.  He's got an American accent and one of his leg is fake.  A bald man with dead eyes.
Speech_0018L=FISHER - A fake leg?
Speech_0019L=MILITIAN - Yes.
Speech_0020L=MILITIAN - Go ahead and kill me, that's all I know.
Speech_0021L=MILITIAN - Go ahead and kill me, that's all I know.
Speech_0022L=MILITIAN - I swear, I don't know who he is.

[P1_1_1_Interrogatetraining]
Training_0001L=(null)

[P1_1_1_LambertComms]
Speech_0063L=LAMBERT - Before you infiltrate the embassy,  let me reintroduce D.P. Brunton, our inter-agency consultant.  He's got an update for the mission.
Speech_0064L=BRUNTON - I'll keep it brief, I'm sure you know,  I'm excited to be part of the team.  The Joint Chiefs want this mission kept non-lethal, and alarms at flat zero.  We can't endanger the hostages.
Speech_0065L=FISHER - Understood.  And with some due respect, leave anything Lambert can say to Lambert.  I don't want the voices in my head to become a crowd.
Speech_0009L=LAMBERT - Get inside  the embassy.  This situation is delicate and largely unknown, so walk softly.
Training_0071L=Use the Movement keys (W/S/A/D) / (Controller: LS) to move. Use Accelerate key (mouse wheel up)  and Decelerate key (mouse wheel down) to adjust your speed.
Speech_0001L=LAMBERT - Fisher.  Welcome back to the front.
Goal_0023L=Infiltrate the embassy.
Goal_0024L=Infiltrate the embassy.
Note_0068L=Hand-to-hand and drop attacks are considered non-lethal.
Speech_0043L=LAMBERT - What are you doing, Fisher?
Speech_0044L=FISHER - Heading out to sea.
Speech_0045L=LAMBERT - What the hell are you doing? 
Speech_0046L=FISHER - Trying to convince you it's time to let me retire. 
Speech_0047L=LAMBERT - That's not funny.
Speech_0048L=LAMBERT - This is not amusing, you're carelessly putting lives at risk.
Speech_0049L=LAMBERT - Get back to shore, Fisher, you've got a mission.
Speech_0050L=LAMBERT - Let's work on stealth. Your gun should always be your last resort. Invisibility is your best weapon. We've got a network of photocells on your suit connected to a visibility meter on your OPSAT. If the meter's at 3, you're lit up like Time Square.
Speech_0013L=FISHER - I've got a man in my way, Lambert.  How flexible is my zero fatality mandate? 
Speech_0014L=LAMBERT - As a rock.  In fact, we want you to make a new friend.  From your on-boards that man looks like one of Sadono's lieutenants.  Interrogate him. Find out what he knows about Sadono's defense parameters.  The chatter we're sifting sounds bad but lacks specifics.  Details on your OPSAT.
Speech_0052L=FISHER - Landmines might spoil my pleasant disposition. 
Speech_0053L=GRIMSDOTTIR - Heaven forbid.
Speech_0015L=GRIMSDOTTIR - Fisher , Activate  your thermal to spot the mines.
Speech_0054L=LAMBERT - Grim's found you a back door.
Speech_0016L=GRIMSDOTTIR - Avoid the main gate at all cost. Blueprints show an ornamental stream running beneath the entrance, looks like a viable way in.
Speech_0017L=LAMBERT - A little wet's better than a little dead.  That stream's your way in, even if it means moving slowly to minimize your noise level.
Speech_0018L=LAMBERT - Fisher,  be careful,  this village is a walk in the park compared to what needs to be done inside the embassy.
Speech_0019L=LAMBERT - Be careful Fisher, your use of stealth is crucial for this operation.
Speech_0056L=GRIMSDOTTIR - The situation is getting worst in the embassy , they seem to kill hostages now.
Speech_0020L=GRIMSDOTTIR - You have no choice that knocking this guard , don't forget to hide his body to avoid a full alert.
Speech_0055L=LAMBERT - Fisher, you are making yourself too visible , watch out.
Speech_0022L=LAMBERT - Damnit, Fisher, We weren't supposed to have any casualties, the mission's over.
Speech_0038L=LAMBERT - Fisher ,  the situation will become almost impossible to control , this operation is based on stealth !
Speech_0051L=LAMBERT - Fisher, you need to hide all bodies in the shadows. The mission is over.
Speech_0039L=LAMBERT - Fisher, we needed to get all the info this guy had. The mission is over. 
Training_0070L=(null)

